name: Thassos
description: The Thassos sectional sofa is the perfect addition with its full upholstery and loose cushions. The sleek metal base adds a touch of elegance and modernity to the overall design, elevating the look of your living room. Its versatile design allows it to be arranged to suit the layout of your room and your needs.

name: Hippo
description: Create a cosy and inviting living room with the Hippo armchair. Featuring a sculptural European kiln-dried Ashwood legs and plush leather upholstery with a large leather cushion with adjustable leather straps, this chair exudes both comfort and style.

name: Hampi Small
description: Sections of the stone pillars of the Hazara Rama Temple in Hampi we reimagined in the form of a series of tables. These can be used as side or center tables and even a coffee tables.

name: Hampi Large
description: Inspired by the stone columns of the Hazara Rama temple in Hampi, this table series reimagines their grace and strength. Combining lathe and CNC techniques with a high gloss PU finish, the natural wood and stone tops reflect South Indian craftsmanship, merging tradition with modern design.

name: Nairobi
description: Introducing the Nairobi Console, an exquisite combination of modern design and traditional craftsmanship. Each console is crafted with quality veneer and European kiln dried Ashwood, featuring graceful legs and inlaid wooden shutters.

name: Nami
description: Nami creates an intriguing puzzle in media storage. Seamless tambour shutters reveal artfully arranged drawers and shelves, with wire management. Mirror finish accents complement thoughtfully composed spaces for modern entertainment

name: Hippo Ottoman
description: Pair the maximal form of the Hippo chair with this exquisitely crafted Hippo Ottoman to match. The light walnut finish of the European kiln dried Ashwood frame offsets the rich 100% Italian Leather upholstery of the seat, making for a statement piece in your living room.

name: Aattam
description: Rock yourself in comfort with the Aattam rocking chair. The armrests are inspired by cane walking sticks of yore, while the frame showcases the natural grain of the wood. Crafted from European kiln dried Ashwood and inlaid with brass, this amalgamation is a playful take on a design that is steeped in tradition.

name: Devon - Queen
description: Crafted from solid wood, the Devon four-poster queen bed features a simple but elegant design that adds a streak of charm to your room. Whether you're looking to create a serene and stylish sanctuary or simply want to elevate the look of your space, the Devon bed is sure to impress. Available in King and Queen sizes.

name: Ciso
description: The Ciso bedside table is a celebration of refined simplicity, fusing sleek lines and functionality. With a single drawer featuring gentle curves, it offers a welcoming silhouette for easy access. This piece fits perfectly against its legs, displaying softly tapering edges and subtle grooves that whisper elegance. The integrated finger groove in the drawer accentuates the table's streamlined look, enhancing its straightforward yet impactful design.

name: Newport
description: Treat yourself to comfort and style with the Newport Bench, featuring European kiln dried Ashwood legs and an upholstered seat for the perfect blend of form and function. The Newport Bench is a versatile and stylish choice for any space. Choose from a range of fabric options for the upholstery to bring a touch of elegance to your home.

name: Luxor without Acryllic
description: The Luxor wardrobe is expertly crafted to bring a touch of tradition to your home. Its exterior is adorned with an intricately woven cane design, complemented by a richly polished solid wooden frame. The wardrobe offers ample storage space with internal shelves and drawers made of ply and veneer.

name: Suvai
description: Experience the elegance of the Suvai table from our Aayutha collection. Its ergonomic high-seating design blends traditional Sangam Tamil aesthetics with modern comfort. With a matte black stone top, brass support, and expertly crafted natural grey stone legs, this table is a timeless centrepiece for any dining space. Choose your preferred brass or monolithic stone stand for a personalized touch.

name: Cam
description: The Cam dining chair combines comfort and style with its European kiln dried Ashwood base and fully upholstered seat and back. Its ergonomic design ensures maximum sitting comfort, while the slender legs and frames add beauty and functionality. With perfectly padded seats and backrests, this chair offers a rejuvenating experience of rest and comfort.

name: Menton
description: Elevate your home bar or kitchen counter with the Menton bar stool. The European kiln dried Ashwood frame finished in medium teak provides a sturdy base while the upholstered seat offers a comfortable spot to sit and relax. With its simple yet sophisticated design, this bar stool fits seamlessly into any decor, adding a touch of elegance to your space.

name: Lyon
description: Tradition meets modern in this European kiln dried Ashwood, ply, and veneer bar unit which exudes a visually pleasing aesthetic. The spacious interior provides ample storage for your favorite spirits and glassware, while the outer frame finished in light walnut adds a touch of warmth and richness to your home decor.

name: Neri
description: Adorned with a captivating tessellation pattern, NERI's design boasts premium dyed veneer, with the grains artistically arranged to create layers of visual depth and sophistication Organize in style with three drawers and a concealed shelved area, all complemented by extra shelf space behind an elegant side door. The piece stands on gently curved legs, echoing Massera's playful essence, and is crowned with a practical glass top.

name: Rua
description: Rua enhances dining storage with visual flair. Two shelved cabinets and five drawers hide behind its floating forms. Mirror finish legs and handles accent the marble top, while clever compartments provide versatile space for dining essentials.

name: Lodi
description: Add a touch of Victorian charm to your space with the Lodi crockery unit. Crafted from European kiln dried Ashwood and ply veneer, this elegant piece offers a perfect blend of tradition and modern aesthetics. The glass and European kiln dried Ashwood shutters showcase your crockery in style while keeping it safe. Upgrade your dining area with this sturdy and visually appealing storage solution.

name: Madhusala
description: Enrich your home’s interiors with the perfectly circular form of the Madhusala bar unit from the Aayutha collection. The minimal front and clean lines allow it to blend inconspicuously while the brass legs add an understated elegance. The leather-cladding serving tray and illuminated upper closet ensure this unit is suited for the finest of wines and single malts.

name: Raki
description: Raki orchestrates visual rhythm in bar design. Tambour shutters with integrated handles invite exploration. Inside, a fused glass counter and sensorial storage spaces create an engaging entertainment experience, enhanced by lighting.

name: Zari
description: Zari redefines the bar unit through interactive design. Overlapping shutters create an enchanting puzzle of discovery in this asymmetric form. Inside, a fused glass countertop and leather-clad drawer create a mixologist's paradise.

name: Highland
description: Elevate your home with the Highland bar unit crafted with a European kiln dried Ashwood frame, legs and ply and veneer carcass. With brass-capped legs and handles, it exudes elegance. Ample storage and a built-in wine rack make it perfect for your home bar.

name: Miletos
description: The cane weaving used in the backrest and seat gives the Miletos bar stool a timeless appeal that is both comfortable and visually striking. The long tapered legs offer a sturdy base while the ample seating area makes it a practical and stylish choice for your bar counter or breakfast bar.

name: Tramo
description: Elevate your dining experience with the organic, flowing form of the Tramo dining chair. The supple contours of this chair bring out the versatility of the design, with the European kiln dried Ashwood shifting in girth across the geometry of the frame. The elegantly contoured cushions with their open seating design add a dimension of ergonomic comfort that offsets the natural grain of the wooden frame. Also available with armrests.

name: Ebony & Ivory
description: Enhance your dining room with the Ebony & Ivory dining chair. Crafted with a teak wood frame, this chair offers an ergonomic seat design for maximum comfort. Its sleek and simple design highlights the natural beauty of the solid wood, perfect for any dining room or kitchen.

name: Colmar
description: Experience the Colmar dining chair with its angular structure, and curved silhouette, which offers ergonomic support. Soft cushioned upholstery adds extra comfort, and the angled chair legs add appeal and functionality, making this a must-have in any dining room, kitchen, or study.

name: Cannes
description: Add timeless elegance to your home with the Cannes dining chair. Crafted from European kiln dried Ashwood, this chair showcases flowing contours for a distinctive look. The woven cane backrest and upholstered seat, featuring 100% Italian Leather, combine comfort and style seamlessly.

name: Kelir
description: Experience the timeless tradition of the Kelir low-seating chairs from our Aayutha collection. Handcrafted with traditional materials and brass detailing, these chairs exude elegance. The hidden wheels provide effortless manoeuvrability, while the choice of intricately woven leather or cotton cord back adds a touch of uniqueness.

name: Thames
description: Experience simplicity and elegance with the Thames dining chair. Crafted with a European kiln dried Ashwood frame, it offers sturdy support and durability. The upholstered seat ensures comfort, while the cane backrest and wooden arms add a touch of natural beauty. With its unique design, this chair effortlessly complements both modern and traditional dining rooms.

name: Yokan
description: The ambitiously original design of the Yokan dining table pairs the contoured tabletop with the organic contours of the European kiln dried Ashwood legs. Their asymmetrical design takes inspiration from hand-moulded clay and the side-mounted cross-legs that stem from this are an ode to the childishness of playful expression. The surface of the table features a raw wooden ring pattern while the natural grain of the wooden legs complete the schismatic design.

name: Michigan
description: The Michigan dining table combines style and functionality with its European kiln dried Ashwood legs legs and durable ply and veneer top. Available in 8ft variation, it comfortably seats your family and friends. The tapered legs add sophistication, while the natural wood finish brings warmth to your dining room.

name: Eden
description: Experience ultimate dining with our Eden table. Crafted with a European kiln-dried Ashwood base and durable ply and veneer top, this stylish circular table is both functional and elegant. The ribbed pedestal base adds sophistication. Perfect for any occasion, it offers a comfortable and inviting dining experience. With a timeless design and impeccable craftsmanship, the Eden table is a beloved centrepiece.

name: Mississippi
description: Elevate your dining experience with the Mississippi dining table featuring teak wood legs and a sleek top in white marble option. The tapered design provides sturdy support while the marble adds a touch of classic elegance to your space.

name: Aayutha
description: Experience the essence of Sangam Tamil era with the Aayutha monolithic dining table. The low seating design originates from the traditional style of seating on the ground in a showcase of humility and togetherness. The black matte finish contrasts with the rough-cut natural grey texture of granite to elevate the senses.

name: Jizan
description: The Jizan dining table is a truly unique piece with its stunning design, it seamlessly pairs a naturally textured table top with a solid wood base and legs. Perfect for any occasion, this table adds character and style to your home.

name: Luxor with Acryllic
description: The Luxor wardrobe is expertly crafted to bring a touch of tradition to your home. Its exterior is adorned with an intricately woven cane design, complemented by a richly polished solid wooden frame. The wardrobe offers ample storage space with internal shelves and drawers made of ply and veneer.

Offering a sturdy, yet comfortable seating space with its rich upholstery the Preston bench will be sure to make your space look good & feel great!

name: Reading
description: Experience style and durability with our Reading Bench featuring a metal frame and legs. The solid upholstered base showcases an architectural aesthetic, while the top cushion is adorned with a premium and stain-resistant fabric. With Halo easy care technology, cleaning and maintaining the fabric upholstery is a breeze. The elegantly upholstered pattern makes it a stunning statement piece in any room.

name: Wabi
description: The Wabi bedside table is characterized by its tapered and blunt edges, rounded for a gentle, inviting touch. Its simple form encapsulates a balance of clean lines and functional beauty, with a drawer that opens with a mere finger groove, adding to the table's sleek appearance. Below the drawer lies an open area, perfect for storing or displaying your cherished items. Atop sits a patterned dyed veneer, lending a unique aesthetic that completes the look with a touch of sophistication.

name: Elche
description: Crafted with a European kiln dried Ashwood frame and a durable ply and veneer drawer, the Elche bedside table also features a cane shelf at the bottom, adding a touch of natural beauty to the design. The clean lines and simple silhouette make it a versatile piece that can complement any bedroom decor, while providing ample storage space for your bedside essentials.

name: Soma
description: Soma elevates bedside storage through thoughtful design. Two drawers, one with a camouflaged handle, offer easy access to essentials. The fold-inspired handle and floating surfaces combine with contrasting materials for function and intrigue.

name: Manchester
description: Meticulously crafted with ply and veneer carcass, drawers and European kiln dried Ashwood legs, the Manchester bedside table exudes a sense of serenity and calm. The bevelled design adds an elegant touch and the spacious drawers provide ample storage space for all your bedside essentials.

name: Devon
description: Introducing the Devon side table, a stunning piece of furniture that combines the warmth of wood with a sleek and modern design. Crafted with a ply and veneer carcass and supported by European kiln dried Ashwood legs, this side table is both sturdy and stylish. With its spacious drawer, it provides ample storage space for all your essentials.

name: Dundee
description: Elevate your bedroom with our Dundee bedside table, effortlessly bringing Oxford's vintage charm. Crafted with a durable ply and veneer frame and European kiln dried Ashwood legs, it offers sturdy support. The spacious drawer stores your bedside essentials, while the open compartment keeps your favorite novels nearby. With its long tapered legs, this table exudes unique personality, perfect for pairing with a cozy lamp or a small planter.

name: Birstall
description: The Birstall bedside table is a perfect blend of natural beauty and luxurious elegance. Crafted with European kiln dried Ashwood legs and a ply & veneer frame, it's designed to impress. Available in white marble top variation to add an extravagant touch, making it a beautiful addition to your bedroom. The pull-out drawer offers ample storage space for your belongings.

name: Girona
description: Elevate your bedroom with our Girona bedside table. This circular table is crafted with European kiln dried Ashwood legs, adorned with metal detail, and a ply and veneer carcass. The crisscross metal adds extra support to the design, making it a durable and elegant choice for your bedroom décor.

name: Leeds
description: Crafted with a ply and veneer carcass and a stylish metal frame, the Leeds bedside table combines functionality with style. The elevated hanging drawer offers convenient access to your essentials, and the open storage space below adds room for books or decor. With its clean lines and sophisticated design, the Leeds bedside table complements any modern bedroom.

name: Mildura - Queen
description: Featuring a European kiln dried Ashwood frame with sleek metal legs, the Mildura queen bed is built to last. The upholstered headboard in durable fabric with metal inlay adds a modern touch to the overall design while providing ultimate comfort for a good night's sleep. Its size ensures a spacious sleeping area, perfect for stretching out and relaxing. Available in King and Queen sizes.

name: Dunkirk - Queen
description: Crafted with a perfect blend of premium and durable full-fabric upholstery and legs made out of European kiln dried Ashwood with brass caps, the Dunkirk queen bed features a contemporary design integrating traditional and modern forms. The rich upholstered frame gives a cloud-like padding for a look that's refined and relaxed. Available in King and Queen sizes.

description: Experience the beauty of mid-century design with Magari's Denver King bed. This luxurious piece features clean, minimal lines that exude elegance. The real showstopper, however, is the unique woven cane headboard, which adds a touch of texture and interest to the overall design. Available in King and Queen sizes.

name: Koro - King
description: Koro King Bed is a masterpiece where structural finesse melds with tactile allure. Four poster European kiln dried Ashwood legs rise with carved textures, flowing into curves that mimic the art of bending clay. Picture the craftsmanship of an artisan, each leg a testament to the deliberate punch and carve of their tools. The headboard and footboard, with their soft contours, rest against the legs in an almost seamless bond, reminiscent of delicately joined clay slabs.

name: Dunkirk - King
description: Crafted with a perfect blend of premium and durable full-fabric upholstery and legs made out of European kiln dried Ashwood with brass caps, the Dunkirk king bed features a contemporary design integrating traditional and modern forms. The rich upholstered frame gives a cloud-like padding for a look that's refined and relaxed. Available in King and Queen sizes.

description: Stretch out, relax and indulge yourself in the timeless form of the Amisos Ottoman. The European kiln-dried Ashwood frame with a woven cane base is angled for maximum comfort. The natural teak finish and upholstered seat add a touch of elegance when it's paired with the Amisos armchair.

name: Gola Ottoman
description: The perfect complement to the Gola Armchair. Crafted with seat that emulates coiled clay and a central fold that adds depth. The two rounded wooden legs evoke the same natural fluidity, their union with the seat reminiscent of the seamless joints found in handcrafted clay.

name: Adelaide Ottoman
description: Stretch your feet out on the ottoman when you relax on the Adelaide chair. Exquisitely crafted from European kiln dried Ashwood, the imposing design and striking upholstery make it a great accent piece for your living room.

name: Townsville
description: The Townsville console with its elegant ply and veneer carcass rests on European kiln dried Ashwood legs, adding a touch of natural beauty to your space. With a wide surface, this console provides ample space to display your favourite decor pieces or cherished family photos. Its timeless design and sturdy construction make it a perfect addition to your home.

name: Newcastle
description: A unique blend of contrasting wood textures and bold minimalism, the Newcastle console showcases the striking beauty of natural wood. The simple yet organic design of the top surface pairs perfectly with the sleek European kiln dried Ashwood legs, while the ample storage space provided by the ply and veneer carcass enhances the functionality of this console.

name: Malaga
description: The luxurious Malaga console is crafted from the finest plywood and veneer, with a solid wood base and woven cane shutters that add a charming transitional allure. This console is versatile and provides ample storage space for dining room, media or study spaces.

name: Madrid
description: Add a touch of sophistication to your home with the Madrid console, expertly crafted in plywood and veneer. This piece is perfect for making a statement in both classical and contemporary interiors, with its timeless design. The teak wood base and cane weave shutters add a touch of elegance to the piece, while the three doors provide ample storage space.

name: Record Console
description: The wooden console is reminiscent of a vintage record player with a flip top that can be propped up and side storage for vinyl. Shelves to house sound equipment like amps or pre-amps, make this a complete solution for audiophiles.

name: Milan
description: Make a lasting impression with the Milan Console. This console features a durable ply and veneer carcass, European kiln dried Ashwood legs, and a marble top for a timeless look. The black wooden grain skirting adds even more charm and character to this beautiful piece. Transform your space with the Milan Console.

name: Henderson
description: Experience contemporary elegance with the sculpted Henderson console. Crafted with a ply & veneer carcass and European kiln dried Ashwood legs, this console combines durability and style. Its geometric design adds sophistication to any space. With ample storage, it offers a clean and organised look.

name: Poco T
description: The Poco side table series disrupts spatial expectations through asymmetric design. Glass box shelves float within mirror-finish frameworks, their unique layouts creating visual intrigue. Paper cord accents add warmth to these compact pieces.

name: Nantes
description: Enhance your interiors with a touch of style and elegance with the Nantes side table. Crafted in teak wood, it's intricate criss-cross wooden legs add a modern aesthetic to any room, while the tabletop surface doubles as a useful storage space. The Nantes side table is sure to add personality to any room.

name: Thunai with Stone Top
description: Discover the artful minimalism of our Thunai stone top side tables from our Aayutha collection. With a three-legged construction and brass inlays, these tables exude a distinctive charm. This brass work carries through the design with brass boundaries around the circular outer frame to give it a distinguishing character.

name: Helsinki
description: The Helsinki side table made with teak wood legs, a glass top, and a cane shelf at the bottom. The legs provide durability and the glass top adds a modern touch while the cane shelf offers storage space. This side table is a stylish and functional piece of furniture that is versatile for any setting.

name: Grenada
description: Add artistic flair to your home with the Grenada side table. With its concrete base and European kiln dried Ashwood top, this piece will stand out from the crowd with its simple, yet unique design. This piece is the perfect fit for your garden or casual living spaces.

name: Ibbani
description: Inspired by the tropics, the Ibbani table made of an ingenious combination of a slated wood topped by a layer of fused glass. Light filtering through the top creates an illusion of dew drops in a tropical forest.

The sleek design with its European kiln dried Ashwood legs with metal support creates an eye-catching contrast, while its compact size and lightweight structure make it versatile for any space.

The unique geometrical frame adds a touch of finesse to the overall design, making this coffee table a statement piece for any room.

The Argos armchair is a timeless piece that will last for generations.

Featuring an upholstered seat with a teak wood frame and woven cane backrest, this armchair is beautifully curved and provides ample seating space. The cane adds a unique touch to the design and provides breathable comfort for extended seating.

name: Amisos
description: The Amisos Chair designed with timeless refinement and a nod to the contemporary era, will become a valued addition to your home. The loose cushions for the seat and back enhance relaxation. With sleek and slender bars adding a graceful touch, this unique piece captures attention and is sure to bring an instant charm.

name: Stiletto
description: Inspired by a visit to China and the elegance of stiletto heels, the Stiletto Chair combines ergonomic design with sculptural beauty. Crafted in Teak or Ashwood, its tapered legs and trapezoidal back evoke mid-century luxury car interiors, with plush upholstery and soft cushioning for a functional work of art.

name: Alden
description: Our Alden single seater armchair is the epitome of modern style and durability with its European kiln dried Ashwood structure. The loose cushions provide a comfortable seating experience, making it perfect for relaxing after a long day. Customise the upholstery to suit your personal style and living space by choosing the fabric of your choice.

name: Barka
description: Upgrade your living room with the Barka 2-seater sofa. Its metal base offers a modern touch, while the tufted upholstery adds a luxurious feel. This practical and comfortable sofa features two spacious seats, making it perfect for snuggling up with your loved one.

name: Berge
description: Make a bold statement in your living room with the Berge 3-seater sofa that offers both comfort and practicality. Its European kiln dried Ashwood legs exude sophistication, while the tufted upholstery adds a touch of luxury. Customize the upholstery from our range of fabric options.

name: Tramo with Arms
description: Elevate your dining experience with the organic, flowing form of the Tramo dining chair. The supple contours of this chair bring out the versatility of the design, with the European kiln dried Ashwood shifting in girth across the geometry of the frame. The elegantly contoured cushions with their open seating design add a dimension of ergonomic comfort that offsets the natural grain of the wooden frame. Available without armrests option.

name: Bari
description: Reclaim the opulence of modern style with this timeless Bari sofa crafted from European kiln-dried Ashwood with cane weaving on the armrests. The harmonious combination of warm and cool hues is artfully created by featuring plush upholstered seating, complemented by high-performance fabrics creating an ideal tonal balance.

name: Kalai
description: Designed to be the focal point of your home, the Kalai console from the Aayutha collection features a minimal design with clean lines and a geometric form. The medium teak finish of the frame paired with the stone veneer finish on the drawer is sure to enhance your home's aesthetic. The intricately woven cane shelf accentuates the design while being reminiscent of traditional furniture styles.

name: Kuma 4.1
description: The Kuma series reimagines modular bookshelf design. Wood and glass shelves alternate within solid frameworks, accented by exposed joinery and paper cord elements. Available in varied sizes, pieces combine to create extended libraries.

name: Aydin
description: Discover comfort and class with the 3-seater Aydin sofa The finest quality solid wood and high-quality fabric give this sofa a refreshing personality. Crafted with the finest quality wood and fabric, this sleek and modern sofa adds a stunning focal point to your living room.

name: Aaram
description: Experience comfort and style with the Aaram armchair from our Aayutha collection. Handcrafted from European kiln dried Ashwood with brass details, this armchair features an intricately woven leather cord or paper cord backrest. Versatile and comfortable, it's a perfect addition to your living room or study. Complete the set with the Aaram Ottoman for a cohesive look.

name: Atlanta
description: Elevate your living room with the heritage-inspired Atlanta sofa. Crafted in teak wood with side tables and loose cushions, it combines natural texture with plush fabric upholstery. Choose from a variety of fabric options to make it uniquely yours.

name: Ago
description: Elevate your living space with the Ago sofa, crafted with a European kiln-dried Ashwood base and detailed ashwood legs extending onto the upholstery, giving it an artistic effect. The plush cushions and perfect stitching, combined with exquisite upholstery ensures comfort and durability. Its carefully tapered legs and balanced shapes effortlessly complement contemporary or classic decor.

name: Austin
description: Indulge in the Austin sofa, designed to elevate your seating experience with its compact size making it a perfect fit for small, minimal spaces. Crafted with strong European kiln dried Ashwood frame and plush full upholstery, this sofa offers luxurious seating in a space-saving design.

name: Aaram Ottoman
description: The Aaram ottoman is crafted from European kiln dried Ashwood base with a comfortable upholstered seat that provides comfort and durability. The ottoman lets you stretch out your feet or in a pinch, can serve as an extra seat. Pair it with the exquisite Aaram armchair which is versatile enough to blend in with your space.

name: Akara
description: Akara embodies visual dynamism in dining storage. Its wooden grid framework houses fused glass shelves and concealed compartments. Paper cord elements and textile-inspired surfaces elevate everyday function.

name: Berlin
description: The versatile Berlin two-seater sofa effortlessly fits into any space. With its teak wood and cane frame and comfortable loose cushions, it exudes a simple yet stylish design. Its modest and light design makes it a great complementary piece to upholstered and bulkier pieces.

name: Kior
description: Kior offers a captivating welcome through illusory design. A floating box wrapped in textured glass conceals a drawer for daily essentials. The mirror-finish framework creates an ethereal presence in entryway spaces.

name: Kairos
description: Kairos organises media components with elegance. Clear and fused glass shelves display equipment, while push-to-open drawers conceal accessories. Integrated wire management ensures clean functionality behind the layered facade.

name: Ori
description: A medley of frosted glass and contoured European kiln dried Ashwood, the Ori centre table is the very definition of how organic shapes bring together the playful character of the Massera collection. This clustered centre table is made up of three distinct parts, letting it rearrange itself to fit your living space in a playful way. The rounded curves of moulded clay flow through the design of the legs, leaving a sense of approachable and tactile wonder for your guests to take in

name: Elio
description: Nestle into the Elio Sofa, where comfort is sculpted into form. With characteristic European kiln dried Ashwood legs and armrests, the design seamlessly merges with the frame, reminiscent of clay artistry like a mug’s handle moulded onto its body. Three plush back cushions with a belt detail and rounded edges promise support with a stylish edge. The combed texture of the fabric not only adds tactile charm but also echoes the warm, crafted look of clay. Including three soft, loose cushions, Elio is a testament to luxurious modern living.

name: Kalvi with Arms
description: The Kalvi dining chair from the Aayutha collection is the perfect companion for the Suvai table, an elevated take on the Aayutha dining set. Handcrafted from European kiln dried Ashwood and inlaid with brass detailing that offers enhanced comfort. Choose between an intricately woven leather cord or a paper cord to make it yours.

name: Kibo
description: Kibo creates a sense of suspension in the chest of drawers. Its grooved surface reveals drawers with ribbon-inspired handles, seemingly floating within the form. Mirror finish legs embrace the piece, transforming practical storage into kinetic art.

name: Aswan
description: Unwind in this tufted upholstered sofa with its characteristic European kiln dried Ashwood frame wrapped in plush fabric upholstery for utmost relaxation. Reignite the love for your home with the tastefully designed Aswan Sofa. Offset the arrangement with your favourite plants to give your space a touch of nature’s wonder.

name: Baza
description: Experience the perfect blend of form and function with the Baza daybed. The sweeping backrest features an intricately woven cane, adding a touch of natural warmth and elegance to your decor. The ergonomically built teak frame ensures unmatched comfort, making the Baza Daybed the perfect spot for lounging or catching up on some reading. Customize to match your unique style with a the upholstery selection.

name: Thunai
description: Discover the artful minimalism of our Thunai side tables from our Aayutha collection. With a three-legged construction and brass inlays representing the triple-dotted Aayutha letter, these tables exude a distinctive charm. This brass work carries through the design with brass boundaries around the circular outer frame to give it a distinguishing character.

name: Occo
description: Add a touch of expressive warmth to your living room with the Occo three-seater sofa. The low-back design frees you, offering a versatility of placement within your space. Actualise the contrasting textures that finish the Occo’s visual aesthetic. The fully upholstered design offers unprecedented ergonomic comfort that your guests will find hard to deny.

name: Koro - Queen
description: Koro Queen Bed is a masterpiece where structural finesse melds with tactile allure. Four poster European kiln dried Ashwood legs rise with carved textures, flowing into curves that mimic the art of bending clay. Picture the craftsmanship of an artisan, each leg a testament to the deliberate punch and carve of their tools. The headboard and footboard, with their soft contours, rest against the legs in an almost seamless bond, reminiscent of delicately joined clay slabs.

name: Gola
description: The Gola armchair takes the playful folded-in tubular design to create a cohesive form of plush comfort. The swooping European kiln dried Ashwood armrests make for the perfect statement piece in your living room. Lounge and feel pampered in the Gola’s soft embrace as you take in the richly upholstered design that wraps in its ergonomic design.

name: Aro
description: The Aro sideboard balances display with storage. Floating glass boxes showcase items while push-to-open compartments conceal essentials. Paper cord partitions add texture while creating practical divisions within open spaces.

name: Adrian
description: The Adrian sofa is a modern masterpiece with European kiln dried Ashwood frame and legs that lend strength and style. Upholstered in premium fabric, it offers optimal comfort with loose cushions. The elegant solid wood detailing on the front adds a touch of sophistication, making it a statement piece.

name: Krithi - Daybed
description: The KRITHI Day Bed extends the comfort of the single seater with a cosy, womb-like curve in its arms, creating a seamless, flowing form. Spacious enough for two to lounge or three to sit, it’s perfect for family rooms, offering comfort for solo relaxation or group moments.

name: Warsaw
description: Our Warsaw sofa is the epitome of sophistication and elegance with its attention to detail and sleek silhouette. The European kiln dried Ashwood legs perfectly complement the rich upholstery with striped stitching, showcasing an added touch of luxury. Unwind in style with the spacious seating.

name: Filo
description: Express a facet of whimsical imaginativeness with the Filo daybed. The plush fabric upholstery and tubular low backrest forms the defining character of this unorthodox design, freeing it from the clutches of typical sharp edges and rectangular contours. Softly contoured European kiln dried Ashwood legs complement the upholstered body and add a touch of enviable artistic detailing.

name: Krithi - Single Seater
description: The KRITHI sofa reimagines the single-seater, offering a cosy, womb-like experience. Its dual form of an oval core within a square shell, made from German pine and foam, blends comfort, safety, and space sensitivity in a beautifully functional design.

name: Kalvi
description: The Kalvi dining chair from the Aayutha collection is the perfect companion for the Suvai table, an elevated take on the Aayutha dining set. Handcrafted from European kiln dried Ashwood and inlaid with brass detailing with an open-seating design that offers enhanced comfort. Choose between an intricately woven leather cord or a paper cord to make it yours.

name: Poni
description: Bring home a touch of distinctive whimsy with the Poni console. The rounded organic countertop is immaculately crafted from acid-etched bronze glass, while the rest of the piece features the natural textures of contoured wood. The amorphously asymmetric European kiln dried Ashwood legs take inspiration from hand-moulded clay. Take a glance at the almost weightless and surreptitious cross-leg joinery that also features floating surfaces for displaying your choicest décor pieces.

name: Massera
description: Discover the fluidity of the Massera couch with a contemporary tubular design that wraps around the base. The pipe-like design was conceived from layering rolled-up clay to add an additional dimension and depth to the piece. The couch is upholstered with a soft rib-knit fabric with the grain flowing across the length of the tubular contours. This asymmetric pipe sofa brings uncompromising comfort while expressing the radical non-conformity that comes with the undirected experimentation of playing with clay.

name: Halstatt
description: Add elegance and functionality to your home office with the Halstatt study table. Crafted with European kiln dried Ashwood frame and sleek ply and veneer top, this contemporary table offers ample storage in its drawers. Keep your workspace tidy while working on projects or studying for exams. The Halstatt study table is a perfect addition to your home office.

name: The Queen
description: This finely crafted table feminises the executive desk. The classic wooden top bestrides fluted sides, held up by coloured legs. Ample leg room and deep drawers add utility and convenience, giving the user command over their space.

name: Arivu
description: Arivu, meaning ‘Knowledge’ or ‘Wisdom’, is the minimal yet aesthetically designed study table from the Aayutha collection. Crafted from European kiln dried Ashwood with a natural oak finish with brass supports features removable storage and wooden trays for organizing your workspace, while the footrest ensures your posture remains unaffected through long hours of work. The straight lines and fluidic form take inspiration from the fluidity and geometric aesthetic of the Tamil script.

name: Santiago
description: The Santiago study table is an excellent addition to any home office or workspace. Crafted with European kiln dried Ashwood frame and a durable ply and veneer top, this desk features drawers on both sides of the table, providing ample storage space for books, files, and other essentials. The artistic frame adds a touch of elegance, making it the perfect choice for those who want both form and function.

name: Santa Fe
description: Experience durability and comfort with the Santa Fe chair. Crafted with European kiln dried Ashwood frame, it offers strength that lasts. The upholstered seat and backrest feature premium fabric, known for its durability and easy-to-clean properties, ensuring a comfortable and hassle-free seating experience.

name: Boura
description: Crafted with a teak wood frame, the Boura chair features a unique seat and back design made of cane weaving that adds a traditional yet contemporary touch. This chair not only provides comfort but also elevates the aesthetics of your space with its refined detailing and sophisticated look.

name: Rosario
description: Experience comfort like never before with the Rosario chair. The chair is skillfully crafted with a solid wood frame and upholstered seat in quality and easy-to-clean fabric that offers maximum comfort and support for extended periods of sitting.

name: Cairo
description: Crafted to the finest of detail, the Cairo study chair features a European kiln dried Ashwood frame and a weightless upholstered seat and backrest design to offer comfort in a unique presentation. Cairo is versatile to match any type of setting.

name: Casper
description: Experience durability and comfort with the Santa Fe chair. Crafted with European kiln dried Ashwood frame, it offers strength that lasts. The upholstered seat and backrest feature premium fabric, known for its durability and easy-to-clean properties, ensuring a comfortable and hassle-free seating experience.

name: Kalvi moulded seat
description: The Kalvi study chair is handcrafted from European kiln dried Ashwood and inlaid with brass detailing that offers enhanced comfort. Choose between an intricately woven leather rope or a paper cord to make it yours.

name: Kuma 4.2
description: The Kuma series reimagines modular bookshelf design. Wood and glass shelves alternate within solid frameworks, accented by exposed joinery and paper cord elements. Available in varied sizes, pieces combine to create extended libraries.

name: Marmara
description: A contemporary splendor, the Marmara shelving unit is crafted with European kiln dried Ashwood frame and ply and veneer shelves. Its minimalistic design showcases five shelves that provide ample space for storage and display. With its combination of natural wood finish and simple lines, this unit will complement any decor.

name: Curious Cabinet
description: This multipurpose cabinet comes in combinable sub-modules and is full height. A convenient open shelf at middle height, separates lockable drawers providing discrete storage space from backlit top shelves paned with fluted glass.

name: Mallia
description: Add character to your home with the distinct styling of the Mallia book stand. The intricately woven cane expresses the traditional heritage of the design while the clean lines of the teak wood frame make it a perfect addition to your space. It's ideal to showcase your choicest of books and other essentials.

name: Kuma 6
description: The Kuma series reimagines modular bookshelf design. Wood and glass shelves alternate within solid frameworks, accented by exposed joinery and paper cord elements. Available in varied sizes, pieces combine to create extended libraries.

name: Lisbon
description: Set the stage for a display of your choicest of ornaments and memories in your home with the Lisbon shelf. This solid wood shelf is instantly desirable to anyone who sets their eyes upon it. This high-end shelf is crafted from the finest solid wood, with ply and veneer shelves and a drawer with ample storage.

name: Lima
description: The Lima shelving unit features a ply and veneer carcass with drawers and metal inlays, and a sturdy metal base. Its sophisticated design boasts laminated patterns that are expertly complemented with brass inlays and handles, adding a touch of understated elegance to any room.

name: Madison
description: Elevate your bedroom décor with the Madison chest of drawers. The combination of a European kiln dried Ashwood frame, ply and veneer carcass, and wooden drawer facia lend a contemporary appeal to this functional piece. With four spacious drawers, this chest offers ample storage space for your clothes and accessories. The sleek, tapered legs add a touch of elegance to the overall design.
